HEADWORD: petitio
<hw>petitio</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Rhetoric, Logic)</fld> <def>The
fallacy of assuming the conclusion in the premises; begging the
question.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> petitio principii.</syn>⟦br⟧
